                  UMS File Name Guide 1.0 (27.05.96)

Guidelines for file names, directories and archives for UMS applications

                   by Ralf Garbade and Stefan Becker

This document describes a standard on an uniform naming scheme for
files, directories and software archives for UMS applications(1)


