PROUD
*****

PROUD is an acronym for PRO-ject U-MS D-ocumentation. It was initiated
to create an structured, reliable and accurate documentation for UMS.
All documentation parts are written in English and Texinfo format.
These source files are translated by @{b}makeinfo 1.55@{ub} into Amigaguide V39
format and linked together within the top node file @{b}@{"UMS guide" Link "ums.guide/Top"}.@{ub}
(crossreferences are also possible).

   Members and supporters of PROUD were/are:

     Ralf Garbade

     hartmut Goebel

     Olaf "Olf" Peters

     Stefan Becker

     ...

If you want to join or support the project with tips, suggestions and
documents please contact Ralf Garbade <d15b@zfn.uni-bremen.de>


@EndNode

